# 🏗️ Smart Land Copilot
### نظام إدارة الأراضي والتوصيات العقارية بالذكاء الاصطناعي

[![CI](https://github.com/yourusername/smart-land-copilot/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/yourusername/smart-land-copilot/actions/workflows/ci.yml)
![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.11-blue)
